# dwm (Dynamic Window Manager)

[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-blue.svg)](https://github.com/a-Nandhu/dwm/blob/master/LICENSE)

This is a customized build of dwm (Dynamic Window Manager), a fast, lightweight, and highly customizable tiling window manager for X.

## Features

- **Swallow Patch**: Applications can be swallowed into the status bar when spawned as transient windows.
- **Suckless Philosophy**: Minimalism and simplicity are core principles, ensuring a lightweight and efficient window manager.
- **Highly Configurable**: Easily customizable through the `config.h` file, allowing users to tailor dwm to their specific needs.

## Installation

1. **Clone Repository:**
   ```sh
   git clone https://github.com/a-Nandhu/dwm.git
   cd dwm
